INSERT INTO `questions` VALUES (1,'What is OneBillionShirts?','<p>Schools, corporations, individuals, etc. all buy custom t-shirts. Our goal is to turn every t-shirt into a vehicle for charitable giving and every customer into a philanthropist. We save our clients money compared to their last vendor and donate 25&cent; per shirt to a charity of their choice.</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:20:27','2013-07-12 20:21:08'),(2,'How does it work?','<p>Our concept is quite simple. We print custom apparel and donate a minimum of 25&cent; per shirt to a charity of your choice. Most clients save money compared to their last vendor &amp; we donate on their behalf to a charity of their choice, which makes quite an easy decision!</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:21:30','2013-07-10 04:12:23'),(4,'What is Save & Share?','<p>Picture this: you go to get your oil changed in your car. &nbsp;There are two stores next door to each other selling the same service, same quality, and same product. &nbsp;One store has an oil change for $25.00 and the neighbor is selling their service for $20.00 and also donating $5.00 to a local family in need of food. &nbsp;Which garage would you pull into? &nbsp;This is the Save &amp; Share concept!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The only difference between t-shirt vendors is the profit margin!</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:21:46','2013-07-10 04:20:04'),(5,'What is the vision?','<p>Leverage the multi-billion dollar custom apparel industry and turn it into an industry model of socially conscious purchasing and selling of goods.</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:21:54','2013-07-09 03:56:29'),(6,'Where do the donations come from?','<p>All donations come directly from our profit margin. Due to our strategic partnerships and volume based discounts we can afford to offer low prices and donate on your behalf, try us!</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:02','2013-07-09 03:30:17'),(7,'Who picks the charity?','<p>The customer chooses a charity. Either choose from our exclusive database or suggest a charity of your own.</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:10','2013-07-09 03:30:36'),(8,'Is OBS a non-profit organization?','<p>No, we run a licensed Massachusetts Limited Liability Company in a socially conscious way.</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:18','2013-07-09 03:30:52'),(9,'Why use a .org domain name?','<p>The .org TLD was established for collaboration and we feel as though our concept relies on collabortaion between consumers, our company, and charities. We all benefit from each other and create an ecosystem of giving which will impact our lives and the lives of others.</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:27','2013-07-09 03:31:12'),(10,'Why T-shirts?','<p>Good question. When we were searching out opportunities to help others on a large scale T-shirts seemed the most fitting. The product is near commodity, the industry is mature, and the need is overwhelming. Most people own 15+ t-shirts, 1 car, 3 pairs of shoes, 2 televisions, 1 computer, 1 phone, ... see what we see yet?</p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:36','2013-07-09 03:31:30'),(11,'How did OBS begin?','<p>Our CEO was saved from a war at age 14 by people involved with charities and made a promise that one day he would somehow pay them all back. This is his way to pay them back.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../../../our_story\">Read Our Story</a></p>',1,'2013-07-04 03:22:44','2013-07-10 04:24:28'),(12,'What shirts do you use?','Just like most all screen printers, we have access to every brand imaginable.  From American Apparel to Gildan and Addidas, we have strong relationships with vendors from all over the world.',2,'2013-07-04 03:22:54','2013-07-04 03:22:54'),(13,'How do you print?','We use the following print techniques: screen print, discharge, direct to garment, sublimation, chino, foil, 4-color process, puff, glitter, and many more.  We’ve been in the business for a long time and unlike most business processes ours is fairly straightforward.',2,'2013-07-04 03:23:03','2013-07-04 03:23:03'),(14,'Where is your pricing?','Our pricing is straightforward and displayed on our website.  Unlike most screen printers, we are not out to milk the customer dry.  We print at a competitive price, donate on your behalf, and are always running contests and bonus programs to help charities even more.',2,'2013-07-04 03:23:15','2013-07-04 03:23:15'),(15,'What is your capacity?','We can print over 60,000 shirts per week spread out across the multiple print facilities.  If you have a large order, we can take care of it!',2,'2013-07-04 03:23:29','2013-07-04 03:23:29'),(16,'How do I begin?','Ordering from us is quite simple and we don’t make you go through a cheesy “design studio” either!  Just select a charity, quickly fill out your order form, and submit.  We take care of the rest.',3,'2013-07-04 03:23:43','2013-07-04 03:23:43'),(17,'When will I get my pricing?','We offer a quick quote pricing system which shows up to date real time prices directly within our website.',3,'2013-07-04 03:24:26','2013-07-04 03:24:26'),(18,'What if I need more than just t-shirts?','We have a full print facility.  Our focus in t-shirts due to the sheer size of the industry and impact we can have but we work with every customers on a one-on-one basis.  If you need hoodies, polos, etc., we will take care of it!',3,'2013-07-04 03:24:36','2013-07-04 03:24:36'),(19,'What if I am unsure of quantity?','No problem!  We deal with races all of the time and understand that you won’t get the actual quantity figures until the last minute.  Just contact us today and we will get you set up so once the figures come in we can act quickly and meet your deadline!',3,'2013-07-04 03:24:45','2013-07-04 03:24:45'),(20,'How do I pay?','We accept all major credit cards, Paypal, check and Purchase Orders with pre-approval.',3,'2013-07-04 03:24:55','2013-07-04 03:24:55'),(21,'What is standard turnaround time?','\r\nOur standard turnaround time is 10-14 business days upon final payment.  If you need it sooner, just let us know and a client partner will work closely with you to make sure that your deadline is met.',4,'2013-07-04 03:25:08','2013-07-04 03:25:08'),(22,'How long does shipping take?','We try to ship from a warehouse closest to you to assure lowest possible delivery cost and time.\r\n',4,'2013-07-04 03:25:17','2013-07-04 03:25:17'),(23,'How much is shipping?','\r\nShipping prices depend on quantity and location.  For a shipping quote, please just contact us.',4,'2013-07-04 03:25:25','2013-07-04 03:25:25'),(24,'Do you ship international?','At this time we only ship within the USA. ',4,'2013-07-04 03:25:34','2013-07-04 03:25:34'),(25,'What shipping courier do you use?','We ship with Fedex & UPS depending on most cost effective and delivery deadlines on an individual basis.  If you would prefer one, please let us know in advance.',4,'2013-07-04 03:25:44','2013-07-04 03:25:44'),(26,'Can you ship directly to my event?','We can ship wherever you want, as long as it is legal & within the USA.',4,'2013-07-04 03:26:03','2013-07-04 03:26:03'),(27,'Do you have a guarantee?','Yes, thanks for asking!  Most custom print companies cannot offer a guarantee due to the nature of the product.  If the product we send to you is materially different than what we promised, flawed by our mistake, or delivered past your deadline, you may return the goods within 7 business days for a full refund or store credit.  Please contact us before sending back.  This may not seem like much but the fact is that once we get product returned, we cannot resell, it is a big leap for the industry!',5,'2013-07-04 03:26:13','2013-07-04 03:26:13'),(28,'Where are you located?','<p>Our headquarters is at 101 Tremont St, Suite 1009, Boston, MA 02108. We print &amp; ship from facilities in MA, UT, KS and service customers anywhere in the country.</p>',1,'2013-07-09 03:34:02','2013-07-10 04:25:40'),(29,'Do you have a minimum order?','<p>As &ldquo;every one counts&rdquo; is one of our taglines used, we try to include all customers but also encourage orders of 48 pieces or more.</p>',3,'2013-07-09 03:43:41','2013-07-09 03:43:41'),(30,'Do you have a guarantee?','<p>Yes, thanks for asking! Most custom print companies cannot offer a guarantee due to the nature of the product. If the product we send to you is materially different than what we promised, flawed by our mistake, or delivered past your deadline, you may return the goods within 7 business days for a full refund or store credit. Please contact us before sending back. This may not seem like much but the fact is that once we get product returned, we cannot resell, it is a big leap for the industry!</p>',7,'2013-07-09 03:45:02','2013-07-09 03:45:02'),(31,'Why get involved? ','<p>Charities benefit from our concept in many ways. Your mission will be exposed to all of our traffic. Supporters can now purchase custom apparel (which we can assure you they do), save money, and donate back to your charity. It is an untapped fundraising stream that did not exist yesterday. And did we mention there is no cost or time involvement, just sign up and you&rsquo;re part of the movement!</p>',6,'2013-07-09 03:45:20','2013-07-09 03:45:20'),(32,'Who can join?','<p>We accept all legal charities.</p>',6,'2013-07-09 03:45:31','2013-07-09 03:45:31'),(33,'How do we sign up?','<p>We make it very simple. Just visit our &lsquo;Suggest Your Charity&rsquo; page and either fill out the charities details or simply enter the charities url and we&rsquo;ll do the work for you. Within minutes your charity will be tapped into this enormous new fundraising and marketing opportunity.</p>',6,'2013-07-09 03:45:47','2013-07-09 03:45:47'),(34,'How do charities get paid?','<p>After each transaction is paid in full and customers have received their order, we either donate online or write a check. All charities have different ways to donate and we donate in honor of the customer each time.</p>',6,'2013-07-09 03:46:01','2013-07-09 03:46:01'),(35,'Is there a maximum donation?','<p>No, we will never put a cap on donations. If 1 billion shirts are ordered, we will be shelling out $250 Million from our pockets, no doubt about it!</p>',6,'2013-07-09 03:46:17','2013-07-09 03:46:17');
